title: ‘Yellowjackets’ Season Finale
description:
Bill, Joanna, and Mallory dive into the season finale of ‘Yellowjackets,’ give their thoughts on Season 1 overall, and make predictions for Season 2. 
Hosts: Bill Simmons, Joanna Robinson, and Mallory Rubin
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
